int max(int a,int b)
{
	return a>b?a:b;
}
int min(int a,int b)
{
	return a>b?b:a;
}

int main(){
	int t;
	i(t);
	while(t--)
	{ int a,b,c,d;
		int e,f,g,h;
		cin>>a>>b>>c>>d;
		cin>>e>>f>>g>>h;
		a=max(a,e);
		b=max(b,f);
		c=min(c,g);
		d=min(d,h);
		if(a>c||b>d)
		{
			cout<<"No Overlap\n";
		}
		else
			cout<<a<<" "<<b<<" "<<c<<" "<<d<<endl;


	}
	
	return 0;
}
